    edenGuideCoordTitle: "Jump to coordinates",
    edenGuideCoordDesc: "Type in-game X:Y coords (e.g. 800:800) in the sidebar Go to coords field and press Go or Enter. The map centers on that point and selects a nearby structure if one exists.",
    edenGuideCoordTip1: "You can also paste coords from the Copy Coords button on a selected structure.",
    edenGuideCoordTip2: "Valid range is roughly 0–1700 × 0–1600 on the full Eden map.",
    edenGuideSelectTitle: "Select structures",
    edenGuideSelectDesc: "With Navigate active, click any gate, town, capital, or temple on the map. The sidebar scrolls to highlight your selection.",
    edenGuideSelectTip1: "You can also pick from the searchable structure list.",
    edenGuideSelectTip2: "Hover shows a quick info tooltip.",
    edenGuideSidebarTitle: "Structure details",
    edenGuideSidebarDesc: "When a structure is selected, set ownership status, guild name, mark as target, copy coordinates, or open Combo Creator.",
    edenGuideSidebarTip1: "Status colors: green owned, yellow contested, red enemy.",
    edenGuideSidebarTip2: "Center and Zoom In buttons focus the map on the structure.",
    edenGuideSidebarTip3: "When team plan is enabled, assign a team, game-time window, and note here.",
    edenGuideFiltersTitle: "Sidebar filters",
    edenGuideFiltersDesc: "Filter the structure list by ownership, zone, type, and sort order. Use the search box below for name/zone text. When team plan is on, a team filter appears too.",
    edenGuideFiltersTip1: "Ownership filter also tints markers on the map.",
    edenGuideFiltersTip2: "Structure search matches names and zones; Enter with X:Y also jumps to coords.",
    edenGuideFiltersTip3: "The list scrolls inside the sidebar — filters and search stay pinned above it.",
    edenGuideViewModesTitle: "View modes",
    edenGuideViewModesDesc: "View dropdown switches planner focus: Strategic (default overview), Scout Mode (intel pull/push), Route Planner (auto path between two points), and Team Plan (timeline when team plan is enabled).",
    edenGuideViewModesTip1: "Strategic is best for general map work and ownership marking.",
    edenGuideViewModesTip2: "Scout Mode surfaces Pull Intel / Push Intel controls in the toolbar.",
    edenGuideViewModesTip3: "Team Plan view highlights the timeline board — enable team plan in the sidebar first.",
    edenGuideMeasureTitle: "Measure tool",
    edenGuideMeasureDesc: "Press M or click Measure, then click point A and point B on the map. Distance respects terrain and shows estimated march time.",
    edenGuideMeasureTip1: "March speed in the toolbar scales travel estimates.",
    edenGuideMeasureTip2: "Clear Measure resets points in the sidebar.",
    edenGuidePathTitle: "Path tool",
    edenGuidePathDesc: "Draw alliance march routes with Shift+click waypoints. Pick a color and name, then Finish Path. Edit waypoints later in Navigate mode.",
    edenGuidePathTip1: "Ctrl+Z or right-click undoes the last waypoint while drawing.",
    edenGuidePathTip2: "Del Path removes the selected route.",
    edenGuidePathTip3: "X1 Targets loads preset objective markers.",
    edenGuideTargetTitle: "Target tool",
    edenGuideTargetDesc: "Pin custom rally points anywhere on the map — useful for staging areas not tied to a structure.",
    edenGuideTargetTip1: "Targets appear when the Targets layer is on.",
    edenGuideRouteModeTitle: "Route Planner view",
    edenGuideRouteModeDesc: "Switch View to Route Planner, then click a start structure and an end point. The tool builds a terrain-aware path automatically.",
    edenGuideRouteModeTip1: "Great for quick what-if routes without manual waypoints.",
    edenGuideRouteModeTip2: "March speed affects the time estimate on the route.",
    edenGuideOwnTitle: "Ownership & guild",
    edenGuideOwnDesc: "Select a structure, then set ownership status and guild name in the sidebar card. Colors update on the map and in lists.",
    edenGuideOwnTip1: "Use filters to show only enemy or owned structures.",
    edenGuideOwnTip2: "Territory layer visualizes north / central / south control zones.",
    edenGuideTeamPlanTitle: "Team plan (optional)",
    edenGuideTeamPlanDesc: "Team planning is off by default. Open Team plan in the sidebar, check Enable team plan, and pick 2–4 teams. Assign structures with game-time windows; the timeline board sorts by in-game clock.",
    edenGuideTeamPlanTip1: "Try it enables team plan and opens the panel — no assignments until you opt in.",
    edenGuideTeamPlanTip2: "Turn on the Teams layer to show color badges on assigned structures.",
    edenGuideTeamPlanTip3: "Switch View to Team Plan for the full timeline; disable team plan anytime to hide it.",
    edenGuideClockTitle: "Game time",
    edenGuideClockDesc: "The toolbar shows live Eden game time (00:00–23:59 cycle). Team assignment windows and march estimates use this clock — hover for the exact time.",
    edenGuideClockTip1: "Same clock as the global time badge next to the language selector.",
    edenGuidePlansTitle: "Multiple plans",
    edenGuidePlansDesc: "Save separate scenarios with the plan dropdown. Use + Plan for a new one, Rename or Del to manage slots.",
    edenGuidePlansTip1: "Each plan keeps its own paths, targets, and ownership data.",
    edenGuidePlansTip2: "Each plan keeps team settings, paths, targets, and ownership — open Plans & export in the control deck.",
    edenGuideShareTitle: "Share & export",
    edenGuideShareDesc: "Share copies a URL with your plan encoded. Export downloads JSON; Import restores a file. PNG saves a map screenshot.",
    edenGuideShareTip1: "Share links let allies open the same plan layout.",
    edenGuideShareTip2: "PNG is handy for Discord or alliance docs.",
    edenGuideScoutTitle: "Scout Mode & intel",
    edenGuideScoutDesc: "Scout Mode focuses on intel gathering. Pull Intel merges cloud ownership data; Push Intel uploads your markings (Firebase, optional).",
    edenGuideScoutTip1: "Try it switches to Scout Mode so you can explore scout controls.",
    edenGuideLayersTitle: "Map layers",
    edenGuideLayersDesc: "Toggle overlays: parchment map, screenshot shots, terrain, structures, paths, targets, teams (optional), labels, zones, territory, fog, heatmap, and sector HD tiles.",
    edenGuideLayersTip1: "Turn off Struct for a cleaner terrain view; Teams is off by default until you enable team plan.",
    edenGuideLayersTip2: "Fog hides sectors you haven't visited yet.",
    edenGuideLayersTip3: "Press R to reset layers to defaults when experimenting.",
    edenGuideTeamsLayerTitle: "Teams layer",
    edenGuideTeamsLayerDesc: "When team plan is enabled, toggle Teams to show colored badges on structures with assignments. Filter the sidebar list by team using the team dropdown.",
    edenGuideTeamsLayerTip1: "Team colors match the timeline board — red, blue, green, yellow.",
    edenGuideTeamsLayerTip2: "Disable team plan to hide assignments without deleting saved data in the plan.",
    edenGuideRefTitle: "Reference opacity",
    edenGuideRefDesc: "The Map layer shows the optimized faction-division parchment underlay (Season 5, cropped and aligned). Use Shots for per-sector screenshots to verify structure alignment.",
    edenGuideRefTip1: "Lower Ref opacity helps when aligning paths to terrain.",
    edenGuideRefTip2: "Capital icons on the parchment are masked — coord-placed sprites are authoritative.",
    edenGuideZoneTitle: "Zone filter",
    edenGuideZoneDesc: "Filter structures by Eden zone: North (N1–N4 staging), Central (C, EC, E, W, WC war zone), or South (S1–S4 staging).",
    edenGuideZoneTip1: "All shows every structure; combine with the sidebar zone dropdown for finer control.",
    edenGuideZoneTip2: "Territory layer tints north, central, and south halves on the map.",
    edenGuideKeysTitle: "Keyboard shortcuts",
    edenGuideKeysDesc: "Speed up planning with hotkeys — most match the tool labels in the toolbar.",
    edenGuideKeysTip1: "M Measure · P Path · 1–8 sectors · F/Space fit · +/− zoom",
    edenGuideKeysTip2: "Arrow keys pan · Del deletes selected path · R resets layers",
    edenGuideKeysTip3: "Ctrl+Z undoes path points while drawing",
    edenGuideKeysTip4: "Escape returns to Navigate and clears measure points",
    edenGuideMobileTitle: "Mobile & touch",
    edenGuideMobileDesc: "Pinch to zoom, one-finger drag to pan. Selecting a structure opens the sidebar as a bottom sheet with a close button. The guide panel stays below the map.",
    edenGuideMobileTip1: "Tap structures to select; open Guide from the toolbar or the link in the empty sidebar.",
    edenGuideMobileTip2: "Landscape mode gives more map room; scroll the structure list inside the sidebar sheet.",
    edenGuideDoneTitle: "You're all set!",
    edenGuideDoneDesc: "You now know navigation, coords, tools, optional team planning, layers, and shortcuts. Reset progress anytime to replay the tour after updates.",
    edenGuideDoneTip1: "Guide v2.7 covers parchment map, optional team plan, and coord jump — use Reset progress to replay.",
  },
